language ESSENCE 2.4.0

given n : int,
letting N be domain int(0..n-1),
given lattice : function (total) (N, N) --> int(0..1)
find C : function (total) (N,N) --> int(0..1)

such that
forAll i,j: N. (lattice((i,j)) = 1) <-> ((C((i,j)) = 1) \/ (C((j,i)) = 1)),
forAll i,j: N. (C((i,j)) = 1) -> !(C((j,i)) = 1)
